verification_code_info.how_do_i_get_body: Kokori omw we nenien pekin tumunun inis, {{healthAuthorityName}}.
verification_code_info.how_do_i_get_header: Ifa usun ai upwe angei ewe code ren an epwe anetata?
verification_code_info.info_body:
Ew verification code ika kapas ika nampa ew code ewe pekin a tutumunu epetin semwenin inisum, {{healthAuthorityName}}, ika pwe a pwarata pwe a uruk semwen.

Ewe verification code e eaea ren an epwe pwarata pwe om chekin semwen mi pung oh mi enet.

Ew me ew verification code epwe tano manemanin non ekis fansoun ren an epwe pwarata pwe met pungun chekin semwen minen nom resap chuen pwan katonong.

Ika pwe e osukosuk nupwen om tinanong noum verification code (nampa ika kapas), kopwe angeni ew minefon code seni ewe pekin ra tutumunu pekin semwen mwen kopwe pwan pwan tini sefaninong.
verification_code_info.info_header: Met verification code (kapas ika nampa e anetata ika io en)?
verification_code_info.what_happens_body:
Nupwen om tinanong noum verification code (kapas ika nampa), ew app epwe aisinuk ren om kopwe pwarano ekewe esenifinifin exposure keys ese fat seni io seni ekoch fon en mi pwan kochu ngeni.

Ika pwe ke mutata, ewe app epwe tini ekei keys ngeni ewe nenien isoisen poraus ren katoun esinesin ren Pwa Ngeni. Ewe nenien katoun esinesin epwe esinesin ngeni ekew fon en mi chu ngeni ren an uruk semwen.

Ewe app ese angei ika iseni porousom  Ekewe chok key ese fat ran nomw non noum we device ra no ngeni emon me emon
verification_code_info.what_happens_header: Met a fis nupwen ua uwanong ai we code?

protect_privacy.body_1: Ekei IDs ese anomu poraus fan itan emon me siwini iteitan 10-20 minich ren an esap pwano ngang io.
protect_privacy.body_2: Phone ekan ekisiwini sokopaten IDs ngeni ekoch phone ren an eaea Bluetooth ese kon eaea waten power. Ei a mutata {{applicationName}} ren an epwe nengeni fichi met ke churi iteitan nge esap pwata pwe en io, inamo ika ese sukuta on on nei phone.
protect_privacy.body_3: Murin an pwata pwe ka semwenin COVID-19, emon ewe a tongeni pwarata noun we pisekin annet {{applicationName}} ren an epwe checki fichi met sokkun tumunun semwen epwe fis ngonuk. Met sokun ID e keran fis on noum phone a esisin iwe a katonong non nenienapen iseison poraus. Ei foforun anet ren met ika io we e anisi ne epeti repot mi mwaken.
protect_privacy.body_4: Ika pwe ew ID mi esisin a mes ngeni ew ID mi nom non noum phone, ei a pwarata pwe menip en mei pwa ngeni emon mi uri semwenin COVID-19. Iei usun {{applicationName}} ach sipwe sinei pwe en mei pwa ngeni ewe monun semwen.
protect_privacy.body_5:
Ika pwe a mes ngeni ew, {{applicationName}} iwe epwe esinesin ngonuk iwe kopwe pwan angei eururen poraus seni ewe putaen tumunun pechekunen inis.

Iei usun {{applicationName}} an ngonuk ewe pechokunen pwisin ekieki ren pechekunen inisum, tumunun om community, ekei meinisn epwe fis nge ese pwarata en io ika ia ke no ia.
protect_privacy.subheader_1: Ika pwe ka onei ewe Esinesinen Pwa Ngeni, noum phone a chok pach ngeni iteiten-ekesiwini, ID ese nifinifin.
protect_privacy.subheader_2: Phone mi wor me on Esinesinen Pwa Ngeni mi mutata epwe ekesiwin ID ngeni ekoch phone ir mei churi.
protect_privacy.subheader_3: Ika pwe emon kewe chon eaea a ponueta, iwe ra tongeni fini ika repwe pwarta usun tumunun semwenin inisir nge esap pwata ir io.
protect_privacy.subheader_4: Ew phone mei chok iteitan tini esisin ngeni ewe nenien a anomu unesenapen poraus ren ekoch ID mi esisin iwe a kuta meni epwe mes ngeni
protect_privacy.subheader_5: Epwe or esinesin ngonuk ika {{applicationName}} a pwano pwe mi mes ngeni ew ika ekoch me mi pwan esisin ewe ID

guidance.call_your_healthcare_provider: Kokori noum doctor me pioing, pekin aninisin poraus on me aninisin safei on phone non 24 awa.

guidance.drink_water: Un wate konik me ekoch minen un mi faat ren epwe epeti om kopwe kaka.

guidance.monitor_your_symptoms: Amusano ika ka apwangapwangono ika semwen. Nom neimw nge operi met kan asisinen emwen epwe toruk. Kokori noum doctor ika pioing ika esisinen semwen e wateno, noumitiw chok neimw.
guidance.practice_social_distancing: Epwenueta awawai nefinom me ekoch aramas.
guidance.protect_others: Fori ekei ren an epwe epeti ekoch pwe rete semwen.
guidance.seek_medical_care: Ika pwe ka ekieki nge a or om osukosuk semwen ika ka fen mefi apwangapwangono, kuta aninis me chuno non pioing.
